messages.text: Are you really laughing out loud?
Whose fries will I steal at lunch??
I’m glad that’s what this friendship means to you, lol.
Again, are you really laughing out loud?
Yes, Noah! I’m laughing like a hyena over here.
No I’m chuckling like Mr. Georges after the spring musical.
The sheer bounciness of Mr. Georges’ belly is probably the funniest site I’ve ever beheld
LOL how did he become a high school drama teacher?
I think he was fired from his job as a mall Santa.
Me and Steph were saying you should be a comedian today LOL.
Do you want to be the president of my fan club?
Okay, we can make t-shirts after we study for history. Wanna do the library at 6ish?
Yes! I will see you there at precisely 6-ish :)))))))
OMG Dennis Stein and Gabbi Parker.
What is, “people I don’t care about”?
Shut up this is serious dawg
Don’t we have like two months until then?
Ugh do you even know anything?
The capital of Vermont is Montpellier.
Cats are blind when they’re born.
It’s like everyone needs to do this elaborate-ass show of asking somebody to prom.
Dennis made a scavenger hunt for Gabbi and spelled PROM with candles at the end.
They’re always making out near my locker.
Sometimes I just watch them to make them feel uncomfortable.
Why don’t I have a boyfriend to do a promposal like that?
Yeah yeah I know...I just wish I could show my grandma a picture of me and my boyfriend at prom LOL.
Did you see Steph today btw?
She still has my bio textbook.
Nah she was home “sick” aka watching The View at home instead of coming to school cause she didn’t finish her bio project.
I bet she gets asked to prom before me.
Hey my mom can get us tickets to see Anything Goes on Broadway next weekend through her office. Do you want to come?
But I think she’s going to Florida next weekend for her cousin’s wedding
Cool, lets see it. I hear it’s really good.
Can I be your Broadway baby?
That’s a song lyric I think
Jeremy asked Steph to prom ewwww
Aww I didn’t realize that happened. I should text her.
WTF you should not be congratulating her he’s gross
I thought you were gonna ask Steph
Really? Cause like everyone seems to be pairing up but none of us had dates yet so I figured you were planning to ask Steph
She told me she thought Jeremy would ask her.
We’re like the only people who still don’t have dates.
There are tons of people who don’t have dates yet, we have til May.
I was at my camp friend’s house all weekend
Ugh this was the lamest weekend ever
Steph thinks she’s dating Jeremy now LOL
I mean they’ve never been on a “date”
But she let him finger her cause she’s desperate
What? You think they’re a couple? He’s just trying to get her to have sex with him
I just don’t understand why you’re always defending her
She does such annoying shit all the time but it’s like you won’t even let me laugh about it with you
I don’t like talking shit about my friends
I’m just asking cause I feel like you’re in love with her no offense
I don’t even know how to begin
It’s fine Noah I’m not gonna tell her if it’s a secret
No I don’t have a crush on Steph
We’ve been friends since third grade
You’re so mean about Steph I thought you guys were friends
Well I thought you and I were friends
You’re being so ducking weird today
Oh my god what did I do so wrong?
Is that why you’re being mean to me?
Cause you’re like my only male friend who still hasn’t asked someone and it’s getting closer
And like honestly I get that you probably wanted to ask Steph
but she’s taken so you could at least have been courteous enough to ask your other best friend
but ok I guess you’re too embarrassed to go with me or something.
Thx for being such a good friend.
And actually I have a date but I was just waiting to tell you
It’s one of my friends from camp.
You’ve been leading me on since the spring musical LAST YEAR
We spend all this time together and like not once do you even think maybe I might like you?
And I know you’re like cynical or whatever and you act like prom doesn’t matter
because it’s just a stupid excuse to take pictures and put them on facebook
and I’m sorry you read catcher in the rye in Mrs. Maloney’s class
so now you think you have to accuse everyone and everything of being a phony
but it’s important to me and you know that. I’ve told you so many times.
And I know I’m never gonna have a boyfriend in high school, I know I’m not skinny like anorexic Stephanie
but I’m not as desperate as her and I’m not gonna go with a weirdo sleaze just because I think he wants to take my virginity
And I thought at the VERY LEAST u and me could go as friends because that’s what we are
but I guess you don’t see me as your friend anymore and you’re just going to go with some other girl who you went to camp with
cause she probably sucked your tiny little D in the woods or whatever the duck it is you do at summer camp
I know that’s a lot of messages but I have a lot to say and honestly you’ve been a really bad friend to me so I think I’m allowed.
Okay that was crazy I’m sorry.
Can you at least respond so I know that murderers haven’t stolen you from your house?
You don’t know what you’re talking about.
Noah seriously I take it back you know I’ve been so stressed out about college and and everything
And I’m on this new acne med and it gives me mad mood swings so I’m sorry.
You’re not even going to say sorry?
Okay well fuck you too. Sorry for wasting your time. Have fun at prom.
Oh my god I’m so exhausted from last night!
You guys looked so cute together
I loved your matching bow ties!
Collin was so excited to meet you all
I was excited to meet him! Such a cutie :)
I swear to god I am.
